---
description: Navit shipped XML and DTD validation
globs:
  - "**/*shipped.xml"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Shipped XML (`*shipped.xml`)

- Validate against the project DTD:  
  `xmllint --noout --dtdvalid navit/navit.dtd <path-to-file>`
- Keep documents **UTF-8** without BOM unless the project already uses otherwise.
- `navit.dtd` constrains element order and attributes; invalid children (e.g. non-EMPTY content where DTD says EMPTY) will fail CI.
- Changing strings inside `navit_shipped.xml` that are extracted for gettext requires updating **`po/*.po.in`** (see `po/CMakeLists.txt` and `make locales`).
